## ğŸ“‚ Input File Format

> âš ï¸ **Requirements:**

- âœ”ï¸ Input file must be a **CSV file**
- âœ”ï¸ Must contain at least **3 criteria columns**
- âœ”ï¸ First column â†’ **Alternative names** (non-numeric)
- âœ”ï¸ Remaining columns â†’ **Numeric criteria values** only

